&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Skillz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to build, own, and see your impact — join Skillz and level up your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skillz is the competition infrastructure platform that powers real-money, skill-based tournaments inside mobile games. We didn&#39;t just enter the competitive gaming market — we invented it. Founded in 2012 by entrepreneur and inventor Andrew Paradise, Skillz built the category from scratch: the patented matchmaking, identity, payments, fraud protection, and developer tools that make fair, real-stakes competition possible at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skillz hosts billions of casual mobile gaming tournaments for millions of players worldwide and is revolutionizing the gaming industry. By fostering social competition within games, the Skillz platform helps developers build multi-million dollar franchises by enabling real-money activity in their games and providing operational support while connecting players through fair, enjoyable, and meaningful competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, Skillz is part of FIRY (NYSE: FIRY) — a global holding company operating at the intersection of gaming, AI-powered performance marketing, and developer infrastructure. Alongside RZR, our AI-driven ad network, and Beamable, our backend and LiveOps platform, Skillz sits at the center of a compounding data flywheel that no standalone competitor can replicate. 800,000+ daily tournaments. $7.5 billion in lifetime prizes paid to players. 90 million registered users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a high-conviction team of builders who came from Apple, Amazon, Google, Microsoft, Tesla, X, Roblox, Zynga, Samsung, Lyft, EA, Riot, Nexon, Gameskraft, PlayStation, Unity, Scopely, Tinder, Intel, Deloitte, EY, Twitch, DraftKings, Wynn Resorts, and more. We operate like a startup, hold ourselves to high standards, and move fast with purpose. If you want to work on infrastructure that matters — and be part of a team that fights for what it builds — Skillz is the right place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As CEO of Skillz, you will own the full business including P&amp;amp;L, global team,&amp;nbsp; and strategic and operational growth for one the world’s largest skill-based gaming platforms. You&#39;re inheriting a 100+ person organization with real momentum and a mandate to scale: more players, more games, more revenue. You will report directly to the CEO of FIRY and operate as a peer to the CEOs of other FIRY businesses, a collaborative leadership team building three interconnected businesses.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;3073&quot; data-local-id=&quot;27b6b372-b656-4cc7-b8b5-0181e9f74f92&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Vision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and execute the strategic vision for Skillz&#39;s platform identifying opportunities to expand player base, game titles, and tournament formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set growth targets for player acquisition, retention, and monetization, and translate them into roadmaps across Product, Live Ops, and Marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay close to the global competitive landscape for skill-based gaming and ensure the product roadmap reflects player demand across key markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team &amp;amp; Org Building&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspire, develop, and scale a high performing global leadership team across Product, Engineering, Growth Marketing, Live Ops and Player Operations, Developer Success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruit and develop senior talent with gaming/mobile platform expertise and foster a player-first, data-driven culture across the organization&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operational and Financial Leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own full P&amp;amp;L for Skillz, driving revenue

