&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about innovation, gaming, and pushing the boundaries of technology? Skillz is always looking for talented individuals to join our team and help us shape the future of competitive gaming and esports.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Even if we have no current openings matching your skills and experience, we encourage you to submit your resume and information to our talent pool. By doing so, you&#39;ll be among the first to be considered when new opportunities arise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&#39;s what we&#39;re looking for in potential candidates:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion: A genuine enthusiasm for gaming, technology, and our mission to make gaming more inclusive and engaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills: Whether you&#39;re a developer, designer, marketer, data analyst, or have expertise in another area, we&#39;re interested in hearing from talented individuals across various disciplines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: While experience is valuable, we welcome applications from recent graduates and those looking to transition into the gaming industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team Player: Collaboration is key at Skillz, so we value candidates who thrive in a dynamic, team-oriented environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re ready to take the next step in your career and join a company redefining the gaming industry, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please submit your resume outlining your skills and experience and explaining why you&#39;re excited about the opportunity to join Skillz. We&#39;ll review your information and reach out when suitable positions become available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you for considering Skillz as your next career destination. We look forward to welcoming you to our team in the future!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More about Skillz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Skillz, we believe everyone is born with unique skills and deserves to experience an epic win. We understand the thrill of achievement and the satisfaction of overcoming challenges. That&#39;s why we passionately champion game developers and players alike, empowering them to unleash their full potential through the power of competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Life @ Skillz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Culture of Impact: Join a united team of builders, creators, innovators, and entrepreneurs driven by the desire to win. At Skillz, we create value and make a difference in the world.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive Benefits: We value our team members and provide a comprehensive benefits package to ensure your well-being. Enjoy 401K matching, equity incentives, extensive medical, dental, and vision coverage, pre-tax benefit options, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work-Life Balance: Achieving work-life balance is important to us. We offer competitive paid time off (PTO) &amp;amp; company holidays to help you recharge and pursue your passions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perks: We believe in enhancing your work experience. Enjoy daily breakfast/lunch/dinner + snacks, Friday Happy Hours, commuter benefits, insurance, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Skillz?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pioneers of Skill-Based Competition: Skillz is not just any company in the gaming industry; we are the pioneer of skill-based competition. Join us in transforming how people play games and building the home of competition for all.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Impact Beyond Gaming: Skillz harnesses the power of its platform to support nonprofit organizations such as the American Red Cross, Susan G. Komen, the American Cancer Society, the NAACP, and more. By participating in Skillz tournaments, you can make a difference and contribute to causes you care about.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognized Success: Skillz has earned recognition as one of Fast Company&#39;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Skillz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to build, own, and see your impact — join Skillz and level up your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skillz is the competition infrastructure platform that powers real-money, skill-based tournaments inside mobile games. We didn&#39;t just enter the competitive gaming market — we invented it. Founded in 2012 by entrepreneur and inventor Andrew Paradise, Skillz built the category from scratch: the patented matchmaking, identity, payments, fraud protection, and developer tools that make fair, real-stakes competition possible at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skillz hosts billions of casual mobile gaming tournaments for millions of players worldwide and is revolutionizing the gaming industry. By fostering social competition within games, the Skillz platform helps developers build multi-million dollar franchises by enabling real-money activity in their games and providing operational support while connecting players through fair, enjoyable, and meaningful competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, Skillz is part of FIRY — a global holding company operating at the intersection of gaming, AI-powered performance marketing, and developer infrastructure. Alongside RZR, our AI-driven ad network, and Beamable, our backend and LiveOps platform, Skillz sits at the center of a compounding data flywheel that no standalone competitor can replicate. 800,000+ daily tournaments. $7.5 billion in lifetime prizes paid to players. 90 million registered users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a high-conviction team of builders who came from Apple, Amazon, Google, Microsoft, Tesla, X, Roblox, Zynga, Samsung, Lyft, EA, Riot, Nexon, Gameskraft, PlayStation, Unity, Scopely, Tinder, Intel, Deloitte, EY, Twitch, DraftKings, Wynn Resorts, and more. We operate like a startup, hold ourselves to high standards, and move fast with purpose. If you want to work on infrastructure that matters — and be part of a team that fights for what it builds — Skillz is the right place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;3073&quot; data-local-id=&quot;27b6b372-b656-4cc7-b8b5-0181e9f74f92&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
