&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and manage a rolling roadmap of CX and VIP initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Drive on-time delivery of CX and VIP initiatives against agreed timelines, proactively flagging and resolving blockers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Partner with engineering, design, and cross-functional teams to move approved PRDs from concept to build-ready status&lt;/li&gt;
